# Task 6 – Create Tables

## Project
Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task involves creating the two primary custom tables required for the Smart Library Request Workflow application.

## Tables Created

- Book (u_book)
- Borrow Request (u_borrow_request)

## Steps Performed

1. Opened System Definition → Tables.
2. Created the Book table.
3. Created the Borrow Request table.
4. Verified both tables in the Tables list.

## Expected Outcome

The application now contains the core database tables required to store library books and borrowing requests.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- System Definition
- Custom Tables
- Database Design

## Status

Completed
